Body:
Description: Hello,
We recently did the license extension for the EPP product, however, today we are noticing EasyLock Enforced Encryption - Expired warning on the license page and users are reporting that they could not use EasyLock

Can this be reviewed as soon as possible?

Regards,
Karan

What We've Learned Updated: the license file they received did not include their EasyLock licenses.
Andrew sent an email to the proper team and we are waiting for their reply
Next Steps Updated: waiting for the responsible team to reply to the email Andrew Miller sent
